SUMMARY:Ready\, Set\, Move (12 months to 6 years old)
LOCATION:7755 Bayview Avenue\, Thornhill\, ON L3T 4P1
DESCRIPTION:This program invites you and your child(ren) to join us and get
  moving together! “Ready\, Set\, Move!” is packed with experiences to 
 build strength\, coordination\, and confidence. Whether it’s jumping or 
 balancing\, enjoy quality time and staying active with your child. It's a 
 great way to connect with other families and educators.\n\nDrop-in\n\nCent
 re: EarlyON Thornhill Centre\n\nSource: https://www.missioninc.com/cso/yor
 k/en-ca/earlyon/calendar
URL:https://www.missioninc.com/cso/york/en-ca/earlyon/calendar
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
