DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260715T111500
SUMMARY:Toddler Time (10 months to 30 months)
LOCATION:3990 14th Avenue\, Markham\, ON L3R 0B2
DESCRIPTION:This program invites you and your toddler to enjoy fun learning
  activities together. You’ll explore different materials\, play\, and le
 arn\, while building positive relationships. It’s a great chance to bond
  with your child and connect with other families and educators.\n\n**Pleas
 e bring indoor shoes (or socks) for the program room.**\n\nDrop-in\n\nCent
 re: EarlyON Markham Centre\n\nSource: https://www.missioninc.com/cso/york/
 en-ca/earlyon/calendar
URL:https://www.missioninc.com/cso/york/en-ca/earlyon/calendar
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
