SUMMARY:Let’s Create (12 months to 6 years old)
LOCATION:3990 14th Avenue\, Markham\, ON L3R 0B2
DESCRIPTION:This program invites you and your child(ren) to nurture creativ
 ity through easy\, open-ended\, and fun artistic activities. These engagin
 g activities may use common household items and may include arts and craft
 s\, drawing\, painting\, and sculpting. Activities help children build con
 fidence and enjoy creative exploration. Parents are encouraged to join in\
 , making it a bonding experience that strengthens the parent-child relatio
 nship. It’s a great way to connect with other families and educators.\n\
 n**Please bring indoor shoes (or socks) for the program room.**\n\nDrop-in
 \n\nCentre: EarlyON Markham Centre\n\nSource: https://www.missioninc.com/c
 so/york/en-ca/earlyon/calendar
URL:https://www.missioninc.com/cso/york/en-ca/earlyon/calendar
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
