SUMMARY:Infant Massage (birth to 12 months)
LOCATION:3990 14th Avenue\, Markham\, ON L3R 0B2
DESCRIPTION:This program promotes nurturing touch and communication. It tea
 ches parents how to massage their baby\, read their baby’s cues\, and he
 lps with bonding and attachment. Certified instructors will support and en
 courage parents to trust their ability and intuition as part of the proces
 s. It's a great way to connect with other families and educators.\n\n**Thi
 s is a pre-registered program for Birth to 12 months (please attend all 5 
 sessions). Please bring indoor shoes (or socks) for the program room.**\n\
 nPre-registration required\n\nCentre: EarlyON Markham Centre\n\nSource: ht
 tps://www.missioninc.com/cso/york/en-ca/earlyon/calendar
URL:https://www.missioninc.com/cso/york/en-ca/earlyon/calendar
TRANSP:OPAQUE
