DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260804T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260804T110000
SUMMARY:Triple P® Seminar: The Power of Positive Parenting (birth to 6 yea
 rs old)
LOCATION:3990 14th Avenue\, Markham\, ON L3R 0B2
DESCRIPTION:This small group seminar is for parents and caregivers who have
  ever wondered "Why does my child do that?" It will help you understand th
 e reasons children do what they do\, so you can guide their behaviour and 
 see more of the behaviour you like\, and less of the behaviour you do not 
 like. It’s a great way to connect with other families and educators.\n\n
 **Triple P VIRTUAL Seminar 1. Zoom link will be provided in advance.**\n*N
 ote: If you register AFTER July 31\, please email earlyonmarkham@familyday
 care.com to request the link to join.*\n\nOther Triple P Seminars this mon
 th:\n* Triple P Virtual Seminar 2 (Raising Confident\, Competent Children)
 : August 11\, 9-11am\n* Triple P Virtual Seminar 3 (Raising Resilient Chil
 dren): August 18\, 9-11am\n\nPre-registration required\, Virtual\n\nCentre
 : EarlyON Markham Centre\n\nSource: https://www.missioninc.com/cso/york/en
 -ca/earlyon/calendar
URL:https://www.missioninc.com/cso/york/en-ca/earlyon/calendar
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
