BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:5727a9191c405405@earlyon-cal
DTSTAMP:20260722T092411Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260810T093000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260810T110000
SUMMARY:EarlyON Family Camp (12 months to 6 years old)
LOCATION:7755 Bayview Avenue\, Thornhill\, ON L3T 4P1
DESCRIPTION:This program invites you and your child(ren) to experience fami
 ly camp by attending multiple consecutive days. Try new things\, learn new
  skills\, and make new friends while connecting with other families and ed
 ucators.\n\n**Studio Camp**  invites children to explore a variety of open
 -ended experiences using mud\, vintage materials\, water\, and clay. Guide
 d by their own ideas and curiosity\, children will actively paint\, build\
 , sculpt\, pour\, and experiment with natural and recycled materials. Thes
 e experiences encourage creativity\, self-expression\, problem-solving\, a
 nd collaboration while connecting with other families and educators. Pleas
 e note that this program will be available on a first-come\, first-served 
 basis.\n\nDrop-in\, Outdoor\n\nCentre: EarlyON Thornhill Centre\n\nSource:
  https://www.missioninc.com/cso/york/en-ca/earlyon/calendar
URL:https://www.missioninc.com/cso/york/en-ca/earlyon/calendar
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
