UID:f211aaa72980e489@earlyon-cal
DTSTAMP:20260722T092411Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260811T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260811T110000
SUMMARY:Triple P® Seminar: Raising Confident\, Competent Children (birth t
 o 6 years old)
LOCATION:3990 14th Avenue\, Markham\, ON L3R 0B2
DESCRIPTION:This small group seminar is for parents and caregivers. It offe
 rs strategies to help you help your child(ren) to become confident and suc
 cessful. Find out ways to encourage your child(ren) to be respectful and c
 onsiderate\, communicate and get on well with others\, feel good about the
 mselves and become independent problem solvers. It’s a great way to conn
 ect with other families and educators.\n\n**Triple P VIRTUAL Seminar 2. Zo
 om link will be provided in advance.**\n*Note: If you register AFTER Augus
 t 7\, please email earlyonmarkham@familydaycare.com to request the link to
  join.*\n\nOther Triple P Seminars this month:\n* Triple P Virtual Seminar
  1 (The Power of Positive Parenting): August 4\, 9-11am\n* Triple P Virtua
 l Seminar 3 (Raising Resilient Children): August 18\, 9-11am\n\nPre-regist
 ration required\, Virtual\n\nCentre: EarlyON Markham Centre\n\nSource: htt
 ps://www.missioninc.com/cso/york/en-ca/earlyon/calendar
URL:https://www.missioninc.com/cso/york/en-ca/earlyon/calendar
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
