SUMMARY:Triple P® Seminar: Raising Resilient Children (birth to 6 years ol
 d)
LOCATION:3990 14th Avenue\, Markham\, ON L3R 0B2
DESCRIPTION:This small group seminar is for parents and caregivers who want
  to help their child(ren) manage their emotions\, so they cope well with d
 isappointment and stressful situations. Learn strategies that will allow c
 hildren to recognize positive and negative emotions\, and deal with them i
 n healthy ways. It’s a great way to connect with other families and educ
 ators.\n\n**Triple P VIRTUAL Seminar 3. Zoom link will be provided in adva
 nce.**\n*Note: If you register AFTER August 14\, please email earlyonmarkh
 am@familydaycare.com to request the link to join.*\n\nOther Triple P Semin
 ars this month:\n* Triple P Virtual Seminar 1 (The Power of Positive Paren
 ting): August 4\, 9-11am\n* Triple P Virtual Seminar 2 (Raising Confident\
 , Competent Children): August 11\, 9-11am\n\nPre-registration required\, V
